result.name: Cafe Nirvana

reviews.text:
Cozy place, nice little bar, lots of choice for food.
The place kind of old, but clean enough to enjoy your drinks. Good location, right next to the MTR exist

Great little bar. Lot of food options. The beer is cheap and atmosphere great. The owners are very friendly and if you're looking for a place to chill after work then this is a seriously good option. Away from the pretentious Soho/LKF crowd!
This place is a go-to for me, a really great hangout
This bar is an institution in Sheung Wan. Yes, it's small and the toilet is also small, but it's kept clean. The food is good and drinking there is just a joy.
Nice and easy place
